---
import SiteLayout from '../layouts/SiteLayout.astro';
---
<SiteLayout title="Cynchorus — Architecture" description="System design notes for the Harmonic Machine Threshold (HMT) framework." ogImage="/favicon.svg">
  <section class="space-y-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-light uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-white sm:text-4xl">System design / HMT framework</h1>
    <p class="max-w-3xl text-lg text-slate-300">
      The Harmonic Machine Threshold (HMT) framework is a layered constellation of sensing, modulation, and resonance
      engines. Each layer is designed to maintain coherence while scaling across distributed collaborators.
    </p>
    <div class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 backdrop-blur">
        <h2 class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-indigo-200">Layer 01 · Signal Intake</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-300">
          Multi-modal inputs are normalized through adaptive tuning matrices to maintain harmonic integrity.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-indigo-200/80">// TODO: content block — instrumentation schematic</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 backdrop-blur">
        <h2 class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-indigo-200">Layer 02 · Resonance Core</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-300">
          Adaptive oscillators align agent intentions using a library of resonance grammars and consent protocols.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-indigo-200/80">// TODO: content block — resonance algorithms</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-indigo-400/30 bg-indigo-400/10 p-6 backdrop-blur">
        <h2 class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.35em] text-indigo-100">Layer 03 · Transmission</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-indigo-100/90">
          Outputs are encoded into codex fragments, immersive audio, and live dashboards for field teams.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-indigo-200/70">// TODO: content block — deployment & governance</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
